      "options": {
        "content": "## 🏆 Best Models — Live Add-to-Cart Feed\n\nEvery row in the live feed below is a real ATC event. **`source=live`** = your browser ATCs. **`source=loadgen`** = the loadgen funnel (Ollama-only, drives the rankings even when nobody's clicking).\n\n**Demo flow:**\n1. Click an ATC on the NeonCart storefront → watch your row appear in the feed within seconds (`source=live`, with model + quality + $)\n2. Look at the ranking panels — Claude Sonnet beats every Ollama model on ATC + purchase rate, but the loadgen-driven Ollama bars compete for the runner-up slot\n3. The leaderboard table sorts by ATC rate — best converters at the top",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
